Horizon Global Corp.


            
            Horizon Global Corp. operates as a designer, manufacturer and distributor of custom-engineered towing, trailering, cargo management and other related accessory products on a global basis. It operates through the following segment: Horizon Americas, Horizon Asia Pacific, and Horizon Europe Africa. The company serves as OEMs, retailers, dealer networks to the end consumer as a provider in automotive, leisure and agricultural market. Its brands include Reese, Draw-Tite, Westfalia, Hayman-Reese, Bulldog, Tekonsha, Fulton and Rola. Horizon Global was founded on January 14, 2015 and is headquartered in Troy, MI.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




