OUR NEWS
















HORIZON GLOBAL
HORIZON Group Companies, Horizon International Trade and Contract Co. Ltd., Horizon Global Services Ltd. and Geoteam Energy, Mining and Construction Co., Ltd,  are well known companies in Turkey dealing with marketing of high-tech products for Defence Industry, Aviation, Onshore & Offshore Oil & Gas Exploration, Production Industry, Construction and Ground Improvement as well as providing related engineering, consulting and training services to the customers since 1987.

  
